## ANTI-AI-SLOP DESIGN FRAMEWORK (QUALITY REFERENCE)

### What NOT To Do (The "AI-ish" Look)
Apps that look "AI-generated" share these traits â€” **AVOID ALL**:

1. âŒ Using **emojis** instead of custom icons/illustrations
2. âŒ **Buttons with no craft** (default component look, weak hierarchy, missing states)
3. âŒ **Generic system fonts** without hierarchy
4. âŒ **No visual imagery** â€” just text and basic shapes
5. âŒ **One-note surfaces** (no layering, no hierarchy, no material cues when needed)
6. âŒ **No interaction feedback** (hover/focus/pressed/disabled/loading not designed)
7. âŒ **Generic placeholder images** instead of real photos
8. âŒ **Crowded layouts** without proper spacing
9. âŒ **Inconsistent styling** across screens
10. âŒ **No social proof** or trust indicators

### What TO Do (The Professional Look)
Premium apps share these traits â€” **REQUIRE ALL**:

1. âœ… **Custom illustrations** and icons (consistent style)
2. âœ… **Restraint-first polish**: hierarchy, spacing rhythm, semantic tokens (gradients are optional and profile-dependent)
3. âœ… **Beautiful photography** where relevant
4. âœ… **Proper typography hierarchy** (size, weight, color)
5. âœ… **Generous whitespace** and padding
6. âœ… **Purposeful micro-interactions** (professional profiles avoid bounce-by-default)
7. âœ… **Social proof badges** and awards
8. âœ… **Clear value proposition** on paywalls
9. âœ… **Consistent design system** throughout
10. âœ… **Real product screenshots** showing the app in use

### Premium Signals (Profile-Aware)
| Element | Avoid (AI Slop) | Target (Premium) |
|---------|-----------------|------------------|
| Typography | One font, default weights | Paired fonts, deliberate hierarchy |
| Colors | Pure RGB, harsh contrast | Nuanced palette, sophisticated tones |
| Spacing | Cramped, inconsistent | Generous, mathematical rhythm (8px base) |
| Shadows | Black drop shadows | Subtle, layered, color-tinted |
| Borders | 1px solid gray everywhere | Thoughtful, often none |
| Icons | Mixed styles, random sizes | Consistent set, balanced weight |
| Motion | None or jarring | Subtle, purposeful, physics-based (pro profiles: damped; playful: can bounce) |
| Buttons | Static rectangles | Clear states + intentional feedback (pro profiles do not require gradients) |
| Loading | Generic spinners | Skeleton screens, shimmer effects |
| Success | Plain checkmark | Contextual success feedback (confetti only when on-profile, not default) |

